title: Whip it Good
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Organic, Western, Fast food, Take-out
description: A stall at the Fremantle markets selling Cocowhip, a 100% vegan coconut soft serve, which can be served with raw chocolate sauce, salted caramel sauce, raw cheesecakes, nuts and a range of other toppings. Several flavors of cocowhip available, no refined sugar. Can get very busy on the weekend.
streetAddress: Corner S Terrace and Henderson St
